General.Name: V2X Inc
General.Description: V2X, Inc. provides critical mission solutions and support services to defense customers worldwide. It offers a suite of integrated solutions across the operations and logistics, aerospace, training, and technology markets to national security, defense, civilian, and international clients. The company was incorporated in 2014 and is headquartered in Reston, Virginia. V2X, Inc. is a subsidiary of Vertex Aerospace Holdco LLC.
